thread.title: Fresh A400M charge clouds strong Airbus profits

title: Fresh A400M charge clouds strong Airbus profits
text:
Fresh A400M charge clouds strong Airbus profits 1:59pm GMT - 01:50 
Airbus shares surge nearly ten per cent on Europe's bourses despite a 1.3 billion euro hit to the delayed A400M military transport plane clouding higher than expected underlying profits in its latest results. Ciara Lee reports reports.
